{"tid":236623,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「認真post」應唔應該分手？","createTime":"2017-05-10T00:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T14:06:30.000Z","uid":44035,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd319870390ff72019e1b81f64b2a3e4416f4647","tid":236623,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:29:49.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左半年...<br />\n我地都係廿六左右<br />\n<br />\n係佢比我既感覺<br />\n係佢從來冇計劃過將來 我一個月25k<br />\n佢18k仲要攞一半人工黎買點打機<br />\n從來唔儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我對佢真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得咁樣拍拖落去冇意思<br />\n<br />\n我有個男同事想追我好耐 如果分手的話 <br />\n我幾肯定唔愁冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有前晚收夜 同男同事去左飲酒<br />\n講左陣野之後 醉醉地我攬住佢喊<br />\n佢拍我背脊安慰我 果一刻我真係覺得佢好gentle 好成熟<br />\n相比之下我真係唔知我男朋友有咩值得我留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b1b472e5f7439f8543fc773f30151b1b04caf0","tid":236623,"uid":828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"感情就好似板燒雞腿包咁 無左就係無左 剩低既只有回憶既味道"},{"pid":"19cb3428437d134cd31b147b32f7f5b87ba92fed","tid":236623,"uid":18110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"如果佢搵50K，再用一半黎入點打機，你又點睇？<br />\n講咁耐你都係想同男同事一齊啫<br />\n分啦，放過你男朋友"},{"pid":"73f30a34eac8997fa3c6fdf7ae15ecea13588c73","tid":236623,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T00:52:45.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n你都有離心<br />\n發展落去都無好結果<br />\n唔好晒時間 分手啦"},{"pid":"7249044360c918acac5d0a09c272c51758d8687e","tid":236623,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:06:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n你都有離心<br />\n發展落去都無好結果<br />\n唔好晒時間 分手啦</blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3b8eae606f57e896dab18cc58793ac4b9fae94","tid":236623,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s